920 
921 inline void CSolver::AddRes_Max(unsigned short val_var, su2double val_residual, unsigned long val_point, su2double* val_coord) {
922  if (val_residual > Residual_Max[val_var]) {
923  Residual_Max[val_var] = val_residual;
924  Point_Max[val_var] = val_point;
925  for (unsigned short iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
926  Point_Max_Coord[val_var][iDim] = val_coord[iDim];
927  }
928 }
929 
930 inline void CSolver::AddRes_Max(unsigned short val_var, su2double val_residual, unsigned long val_point, const su2double* val_coord) {
931  if (val_residual > Residual_Max[val_var]) {
932  Residual_Max[val_var] = val_residual;
933  Point_Max[val_var] = val_point;
934  for (unsigned short iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
935  Point_Max_Coord[val_var][iDim] = val_coord[iDim];
936  }
937 }

1205 inline su2double CEulerSolver::GetModVelocity_Inf(void) {
1206  su2double Vel2 = 0;
1207  for (unsigned short iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++)
1208  Vel2 += Velocity_Inf[iDim]*Velocity_Inf[iDim];
1209  return sqrt(Vel2);
1210 }

1256 inline void CEulerSolver::SetInlet_Ttotal(unsigned short val_marker, unsigned long val_vertex, su2double val_ttotal) {
1257  /*--- Since this call can be accessed indirectly using python, do some error
1258  * checking to prevent segmentation faults ---*/
1259  if (val_marker >= nMarker)
1260  SU2_MPI::Error("Out-of-bounds marker index used on inlet.", CURRENT_FUNCTION);
1261  else if (Inlet_Ttotal == NULL || Inlet_Ttotal[val_marker] == NULL)
1262  SU2_MPI::Error("Tried to set custom inlet BC on an invalid marker.", CURRENT_FUNCTION);
1263  else if (val_vertex >= nVertex[val_marker])
1264  SU2_MPI::Error("Out-of-bounds vertex index used on inlet.", CURRENT_FUNCTION);
1265  else
1266  Inlet_Ttotal[val_marker][val_vertex] = val_ttotal;
1267 }

1645 inline void CEulerSolver::ComputeTurboVelocity(su2double *cartesianVelocity, su2double *turboNormal, su2double *turboVelocity, unsigned short marker_flag, unsigned short kind_turb) {
1646 
1647  if ((kind_turb == AXIAL && nDim == 3) || (kind_turb == CENTRIPETAL_AXIAL && marker_flag == OUTFLOW) || (kind_turb == AXIAL_CENTRIFUGAL && marker_flag == INFLOW) ){
1648  turboVelocity[2] = turboNormal[0]*cartesianVelocity[0] + cartesianVelocity[1]*turboNormal[1];
1649  turboVelocity[1] = turboNormal[0]*cartesianVelocity[1] - turboNormal[1]*cartesianVelocity[0];
1650  turboVelocity[0] = cartesianVelocity[2];
1651  }
1652  else{
1653  turboVelocity[0] = turboNormal[0]*cartesianVelocity[0] + cartesianVelocity[1]*turboNormal[1];
1654  turboVelocity[1] = turboNormal[0]*cartesianVelocity[1] - turboNormal[1]*cartesianVelocity[0];
1655  if (marker_flag == INFLOW){
1656  turboVelocity[0] *= -1.0;
1657  turboVelocity[1] *= -1.0;
1658  }
1659  if(nDim == 3)
1660  turboVelocity[2] = cartesianVelocity[2];
1661  }
1662 }
1663 
1664 inline void CEulerSolver::ComputeBackVelocity(su2double *turboVelocity, su2double *turboNormal, su2double *cartesianVelocity, unsigned short marker_flag, unsigned short kind_turb){
1665 
1666  if ((kind_turb == AXIAL && nDim == 3) || (kind_turb == CENTRIPETAL_AXIAL && marker_flag == OUTFLOW) || (kind_turb == AXIAL_CENTRIFUGAL && marker_flag == INFLOW)){
1667  cartesianVelocity[0] = turboVelocity[2]*turboNormal[0] - turboVelocity[1]*turboNormal[1];
1668  cartesianVelocity[1] = turboVelocity[2]*turboNormal[1] + turboVelocity[1]*turboNormal[0];
1669  cartesianVelocity[2] = turboVelocity[0];
1670  }
1671  else{
1672  cartesianVelocity[0] = turboVelocity[0]*turboNormal[0] - turboVelocity[1]*turboNormal[1];
1673  cartesianVelocity[1] = turboVelocity[0]*turboNormal[1] + turboVelocity[1]*turboNormal[0];
1674 
1675  if (marker_flag == INFLOW){
1676  cartesianVelocity[0] *= -1.0;
1677  cartesianVelocity[1] *= -1.0;
1678  }
1679 
1680  if(nDim == 3)
1681  cartesianVelocity[2] = turboVelocity[2];
1682  }
1683 }

2448 inline void CTurbSolver::SetInlet_TurbVar(unsigned short val_marker, unsigned long val_vertex, unsigned short val_dim, su2double val_turb_var) {
2449  /*--- Since this call can be accessed indirectly using python, do some error
2450  * checking to prevent segmentation faults ---*/
2451  if (val_marker >= nMarker)
2452  SU2_MPI::Error("Out-of-bounds marker index used on inlet.", CURRENT_FUNCTION);
2453  else if (Inlet_TurbVars == NULL || Inlet_TurbVars[val_marker] == NULL)
2454  SU2_MPI::Error("Tried to set custom inlet BC on an invalid marker.", CURRENT_FUNCTION);
2455  else if (val_vertex >= nVertex[val_marker])
2456  SU2_MPI::Error("Out-of-bounds vertex index used on inlet.", CURRENT_FUNCTION);
2457  else if (val_dim >= nVar)
2458  SU2_MPI::Error("Out-of-bounds index used for inlet turbulence variable.", CURRENT_FUNCTION);
2459  else
2460  Inlet_TurbVars[val_marker][val_vertex][val_dim] = val_turb_var;
2461 }
